---
title: Lemon Chicken & Creamy Dill-Caper Sauce with Prosciutto-Roasted Veggies
description: This dish features the key to a crowd-pleasing dinner: sauce! Who could turn down a drizzly dill and caper concoction, especially
one that’s draped across pan-seared chicken, roasted potatoes and greens? No one, we say. At least, not anyone we’ve met. So
get ready for the creamiest, most showstopping sauce celebration you have experienced yet.
